headline: Galileo Announces Free Agent Reliability Platform
summary: Galileo, the leading AI reliability platform trusted for evaluations and observability by global enterprises including HP, Twilio, Reddit, and Comcast, today announced the launch of its comprehensive platform update for AI agent reliability, free for developers around the world. As AI agents become increasingly autonomous and multi-step, traditional evaluation tools struggle to detect their complex failure modes. Galileo's new agent reliability solution is purpose-built for multi-agent AI system
